# 🔐 Project 1: Investigating Suspicious Login Attempts (Brute Force Case)

**Role:** Tier 1 Security Analyst  
**Scenario:** Multiple failed login alerts were triggered overnight. You have been tasked with analysing the authentication logs to identify suspicious activity, detect attack patterns, and determine if any accounts were compromised.

---

## 🖥️ Environment & Tools Used

| Tool | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| Windows 10/11 | Operating system |
| VS Code | Code editor for writing and running Python |
| Python 3 | Programming language |
| Python Extension for VS Code | Running Python scripts inside VS Code |
| pandas | Building and exporting the dataset |
| faker | Generating realistic fake data |
| MySQL | Running investigation queries on the dataset |

